org.nashua.tt151.libraries.parsers

Class ValueParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nashua.tt151.libraries.parsers.ValueParser

  • public final class ValueParser
extends Object
    A class containing methods for converting doubles and ints to adhere to the protocol. The class can convert doubles and integers to message-format and contains wrappers for safely parsing strings

    1.1
